title: Martín Tejera
text:
Martín Tejera Vázquez (born 16 February 1991) is an Uruguayan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for the reserve team of SC Fortuna Köln.


== Career ==
On 30 December 2019 it was confirmed, that Tejera had joined the reserve team of SC Fortuna Köln.


== Honours ==


=== Club ===
NacionalUruguayan Primera División (3): 2008–09, 2010–11, 2011–12
